<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1. Isu kawmah ka kipumpiek,
 Kiphal takin ka kipiei;
 Amah hehpih, taksang zing ka,
 Nicheng in Amah zui ka.

[V2]
 Ka kipumpiek hi, Ka kipumpiek hi,
 Hukdampa deihum, Nang kawmah,
 Ka kipumpiek hi.

[V3]
 2. Isu kawmah ka kipumpiek,
 A kengbul ah ka khun hi;
 Khawvel nawpna cheng ka nusie'i,
 Lal Isu, tun ei puiin.

[V4]
 3. Isu kawmah ka kipumpiek,
 Hukdampa Nang ei neiin;
 Kei Nanga, Nang keia Na hih,
 Thagau in ei hetsak hen.

[V5]
 4. Isu kawmah ka kipumpiek,
 Lalpa, Nang din ka kipiei;
 Hehpih, hatnan ei hih dimin,
 Na vangsaknan ei vukin.

[V6]
 5. Isu kawmah ka kipumpiek,
 Tun a nawpzie ka he tai;
 Hukdamna bukim kipahna,
 Lopi! lopi hen A min!</lyrics>
<title>ALL TO JESUS I SURRENDER</title>
<hymn_number>357</hymn_number>
</song>